<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="let-in">let … in</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>让…进来；放进：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The theatre was so small that they refused to let in any more people. 
剧院太小了，所以他们不让更多的人进来。</p><footer>北师大④ – 12</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I opened our bedroom windows to let in the wind. 
我打开了我们卧室的窗户通风。</p><footer>2009 福建改</footer></div></div>